            <h2>
                   <strong> Scholarship Description:</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                            Foundation For Excellence Scholarship 2018-19 invites applications from meritorious students enrolled in the 1st year of BE/B.Tech, MBBS  or 5-year Integrated M.Tech Dual Degree program for the academic year 2018-19. The scholarship aims to provide financial and other assistance to meritorious and needy students who wish to study professional degree courses.
                            The scholarship is being provided by the Foundation For Excellence (FFE). The selected candidates will be awarded with financial and other assistance under this scholarship scheme. 
                           </p>
                            <h2>
                                <hr>
                                    <strong>Eligibility for the Scholarship:</strong>
                                    </h2>
 <p>
 
        To be eligible for the scholarship, an applicant must -
<ul>
<li>	Be enrolled in the 1st year of BE, B.Tech, MBBS or 5-year Integrated M.Tech dual degree program in the year 2018-19. </li>
<li> Have passed Intermediate/Higher Secondary/Pre-University/ISC/CBSE or other equivalent board qualifying examination no earlier than 2017 with at least 70 percent marks or more.    </li>
<li>Have taken admission to a professional degree course in engineering, technology or medicine on the basis of general/open merit rank of state/national level entrance examination or through a counseling conducted at the state level. </li>
<li>Have gross annual family income not more than INR 2.5 Lakh from all sources. </li>

</ul>
<strong>Note:</strong>The diploma students taking lateral admission to BE or B.Tech courses and students of B.Arch, BDS and B.Pharma are not eligible to apply for the scholarship. 
</p>
