                                          </p>
                                            <h2>
                                                <hr>
                                                <strong>Documents required for the Scholarship: </strong>
                                                </h2>
                                                <p>
                                                    <ul>
                                                        <li>If the parents of an applicant are employees, he/she needs to provide a certified salary/pay slip from the employer containing all details about his/her basic salary and all deductions and allowances. </li>
                                                        <li>If an applicant's parents are retirees or pensioners, he/she needs to provide a pension statement issued by the pension authority and/or by an authorised bank. </li>
                                                        <li>Aadhaar Card (if Aadhaar Card is not available, an equivalent document for proof of address)</li>
                                                        <li>If an applicant's parents are self-employed or hold a business, they need to provide income certificate issued by an authorised government official or income tax return specifying the gross family income. </li>
                                                        <li>The students of agriculturalists, cultivators or farmers need to provide an income certificate issued by a competent or recognised authority. They also need to provide the details of size and nature of landholding crops grown.</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                </p>
